# Windsurf AI Rules — P-MAS-v2 Project

## Product
P-MAS-v2: Prompt-based Multi-Agent System Dashboard.
26 AI agents across 8 role groups (Strategy, Tactics, Control, Execution,
Memory, Monitoring, Communication, Learning).

## Architecture
```
src/app/              Pages
src/components/
  hierarchy/          Agent Hierarchy (React Flow + Dagre DAG)
  workflows/          Workflow Pipeline
  ui/                 shadcn/ui base
src/hooks/            Custom hooks
src/lib/              Utils, Prisma, API helpers
prisma/               Schema and seed
```

## Design
- Black #000000 background, Cyan #06B6D4 accent, monochrome
- React Flow for hierarchy DAG, Framer Motion for animations

## Anti-Monolith Rules
1. Component <= 150 lines, File <= 200 lines, Page <= 40 lines
2. Max 3 useState -> extract to hook
3. No data fetching in components
4. Barrel exports always
5. Static imports only (Turbopack)
6. ESLint layer separation active

## Import Patterns
- `import { AgentNode } from '@/components/hierarchy/agent-node'`
- `import { WorkflowCard } from '@/components/workflows/workflow-card'`
- `import { db } from '@/lib/db'`
- `import { fetchWithRetry } from '@/lib/client-fetch'`

## API
/api/agents, /api/agents/prompt, /api/tasks, /api/hierarchy,
/api/stats, /api/health, /api/seed

## Stack
Next.js 16, React 19, TypeScript 5, Tailwind CSS 4, shadcn/ui,
Prisma SQLite, React Flow, Framer Motion, Zustand
